info.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 09 at 2:10AM PST until January 09 at 10:00PM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 PM PST THIS EVENING... * WHAT...South winds 25 to 40 mph with gusts to 65 mph are expected. * WHERE...Santa Ynez Mountains Western Range and Santa Ynez Mountains Eastern Range. * WHEN...Until 10 PM PST this evening. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds may blow down trees and power lines, possibly causing power outages. Travel will be difficult, especially for drivers of high profile vehicles.
info.instruction: People should avoid being outside in forested areas and around large trees. If possible, stay in your home during the windstorm, and avoid windows. Use caution if you must drive.
